# Phase 2 + Phase 4 (#232) generated-test artifacts.
#
# The committed golden manifests and the generator sources are normalized to LF
# in the index so a Windows-authored commit and a Linux CI run regenerate them
# byte-for-byte identically — keeping the `--check` determinism gate stable
# across platforms regardless of each developer's core.autocrlf setting. (The
# generator's `check_artifact` also normalizes CRLF on read, so this is
# defense-in-depth; it additionally keeps the committed goldens diff-clean.)
*.json text eol=lf
*.sql text eol=lf
generator/src/*.rs text eol=lf
